                     <p>This manuscript was copied by  <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10036Wansleb">Johann-Michael Wansleben</persName> in <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2085Cairo">Cairo</placeName>. 
