                     <p>He either took it back after donating it to the library of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3201CosimoI">Cosimo III</persName> as indicated by <ref target="#a16"/> or never donated it, since it came to the <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0303BNF">Bibliothèque nationale de France</placeName> 
